imdb.plot outline: The series recounts the life and adventures of the Podcats, four video game characters both musicians and "mini geeks" who live happily in the digital universe at the disposition of today's youngsters. It's a totally original and interconnected TV format aimed at the interests of today's youngsters between six and twelve years old, i.e; video games and music.
imdb.title: The Podcats
plot: The series recounts the life and adventures of the Podcats, four video game characters both musicians and "mini geeks" who live happily in the digital universe at the disposition of today's youngsters. It's a totally original and interconnected TV format aimed at the interests of today's youngsters between six and twelve years old, i.e; video games and music.
